distribute(address[]).details: this function is used in case some distribution fails

distribute(uint256,uint256).details: this function is used in case we have too many targets and gasLimit is reached

params.finish: finish index point of the targets array
params.start: start index point of the targets array

distributeFees(address[]).details: the gauge is the owner of the LPs so it has to claim

params._gauges: gauge address where to claim the fees

notifyRewardAmount(uint256).details: the function is called by the minter each epoch. Anyway anyone can top up some extra rewards.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._weights: array of weights for each gauge target

claimBribes(address[],address[][]).notice: claim bribes rewards given an address

claimBribes(address[],address[][],uint25.notice: claim bribes rewards given a TokenID

claimFees(address[],address[][]).notice: claim fees rewards given an address

claimFees(address[],address[][],uint256).notice: claim fees rewards given a TokenID

distribute(address[]).notice: distribute reward onyl for given gauges

distribute(uint256,uint256).notice: distribute the emission for N gauges

distributeAll().notice: Distribute the emission for ALL gauges

distributeFees(address[]).notice: distribute the LP Fees to the internal bribes

increaseGaugeApprovals(address).notice: Increase gauge approvals if max is type(uint).max is reached    [very long run could happen]

length().notice: view the total length of the targets

poke(uint256).notice: Recast the saved votes of a given TokenID

reset(uint256).notice: Reset the votes of a given TokenID

setExternalBribeFor(address,address).notice: Set a new External bribe for a given gauge

setInternalBribeFor(address,address).notice: Set a new internal bribe for a given gauge

setNewBribes(address,address,address).notice: Set a new bribes for a given gauge

targetVoteLength(uint256).notice: view the total length of the voted targets given a tokenId
